{
    "name": "Crime Lord",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Though most criminal masterminds work behind the scenes, crime lords don\u2019t mind getting their hands dirty."
        },
        {
            "name": "Tontelizi Legbreaker",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "When Tontelizi first took to a life of crime, he was relegated to leg-breaking as a joke on his slight stature\u2014and collections doubled. Soon, the crime family found that Tontelizi excelled at any task involving extortion, intimidation, or violence. When the patriarch\u2019s health failed\u2014assisted by Tontelizi\u2019s poison\u2014the gnome eliminated two likely successors and cowed the rest with threats and blackmail. He was chosen to take over the family with nearly unanimous support."
        }
    ],
